{"tid":1916164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如我哋睇下梁天琦除咗講 光復香港時代革命 仲講過咩","createTime":"2020-03-08T17:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T06:31:42.000Z","uid":34515,"like":205,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ab93d67490cfa93243065439200a4bc1d2ce56","tid":1916164,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNH9xKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNH9xKX.jpg&h=0f41f738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知好多人會覺得 全民勇武就一早光復咗香港啦<br />\n呢句説話其實有好幾個問題<br />\n咩係光復香港 點解你覺得你嘅光復香港同其他人一樣<br />\n如果唔一樣 點解你覺得人地要做同你一樣嘅嘢去光復你心目中想要嘅香港？<br />\n<br />\n無論係有部分前線嘅諗法 定facebook有部分超淺黃嘅諗法<br />\n我都覺得冇問題 你要打狗界狗燒狗都好 你覺得有用就做<br />\n你覺得選立法會可以慢慢改變制度 你做<br />\n<br />\n係可以冇衝突<br />\n係可以一齊做<br />\n<br />\n同路人心底都係唔想香港變成中國<br />\n因為企喺呢邊嘅 開頭都係因為反修例同警暴企同一陣線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要大方向一樣 我哋就係同路人<br />\n深藍都未屌到咁金 屌同路人屌到開花有咩幫助？</span><br />\n<br />\n最後 勇武們<br />\n抱歉嘅係香港人真係未夠你哋心目中嘅勇武<br />\n但希望你唔好因爲咁放棄用自己方法爭取自己想要嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n其他人 老實講 的確有好大進步空間<br />\n仲有好多嘢可以做 特別係tvb同youtuber同twitter <br />\n長期唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線心灰都係情有可原<br />\n但宜家開始大家可唔可以做多啲 俾返多啲希望前線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得共同體？</span><br />\n<br />\n站喺對方立場 感受對方嘅痛苦<br />\n作為命運共同體 坐同一條船 我哋就要一齊行到最後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119a14e0e0e0a7f77bd2142c7823c06b93930201","tid":1916164,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"無撚有錯"},{"pid":"b5f52dc2d7450aa73706c321f274105773aacc17","tid":1916164,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"連登仔要將憤怒發洩係港共身上，唔好亂用來批鬥其他人浪費心力"},{"pid":"2580fd1bce1c64b463e1218ae97c0f668b0a9674","tid":1916164,"uid":69221,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"仲講過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民主黨 賣香港</span>"},{"pid":"a1f5490e39b2aeac48a3c9f991f22558b3e885df","tid":1916164,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"用自己覺得可以做到嘅方式堅持下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不放棄"},{"pid":"3af156f881db326c3ae140a8592985e5f79b2e11","tid":1916164,"uid":69221,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"仲講過要唾棄形式主義，教條主義<br />\n<br />\n販民揸旗咁多年就係一直形式主義扮爭取<br />\n得閒助攻下建制"},{"pid":"87b55ce45cf5cae42072cd8b20ed01b84db0a995","tid":1916164,"uid":10954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"無論用咩方法，只要目標一致都要去做"},{"pid":"349d577c651e427d423daee62015e0881e2546d7","tid":1916164,"uid":292151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋幾耐冇聽過 兄弟爬山 各自努力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"05c7bb549746118846cd5abd7c01fa70b599bc41","tid":1916164,"uid":269686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c584ae57a780b3276177d15a6ddbfede21aed88b","tid":1916164,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15ba0628d7ae4463c11f20ad7ac2092607eca454","tid":1916164,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:43:38.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5beeae3d10fb025369f91627a2e0fb0707de6ec","tid":1916164,"uid":160912,"like":4,"d